WIMPY / WHIMPY: Automatic flee threshold

Syntax:
  wimpy                 show current setting
  wimpy <1-90>          auto-flee below this % of max HP
  wimpy on              enable at 25%
  wimpy off             disable auto-flee

  whimpy                same command (alternate spelling)

DESCRIPTION:
  When auto-flee is active, you attempt to flee combat when your HP
  drops below the given percentage. A single hit can still drop you
  below the threshold before flee triggers.

SEE ALSO: flee, combat, score
